{"id":232437803,"title":"［調酒］教父🇮🇹","content":"https://i.imgur.com/G4r4UtF.jpg\n「仁慈的父，我已墜入，看不見『醉』的國度」\n教父，一個經典的代名詞\n電影上，浮現馬龍白蘭度入木三分的演技\n音樂上，響起杰倫華麗古典的以父之名\n調酒上，一樣有他的地位\n因為加入義大利香甜酒\n聯想到義大利黑手黨而得名\n是一款非常經典的調酒\n\n酒譜：\n裸雀威士忌 The naked grouse whiskey  45ml\n迪沙羅娜杏仁酒 Disaronno 15ml\n\n調法：攪拌法\n\n口感：\n\n教父，威士忌中加入杏仁酒\n選對威士忌跟抓好杏仁酒比例\n原則上不會太難喝\n\n這次使用裸雀威士忌\n威士忌的本身的櫻桃香氣以及巧克力味跟杏仁甜很搭\n像在吃甜點一樣\n杏仁甜中帶一點巧克力微苦\n超推薦大家買來嘗試\n\nBy gin_wei\n\n一個不專業的調酒初學者\n喜歡我的文章可以追蹤我的IG\n會不定時分享一些跑酒吧、自己調酒、品酒會心得\nhttps://www.instagram.com/p/B4cnRVAFVsd/?igshid=6a2k8zl9qowq","excerpt":"「仁慈的父，我已墜入，看不見『醉』的國度」教父，一個經典的代名詞，電影上，浮現馬龍白蘭度入木三分的演技，音樂上，響起杰倫華麗古典的以父之名，調酒上，一樣有他的地位，因為加入義大利香甜酒，聯想到義大利黑","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"23082c2f-c19d-456c-a805-1e6ac0a36c31","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-11-04T14:39:18.019Z","updatedAt":"2019-11-04T14:39:18.019Z","commentCount":3,"likeCount":36,"tags":[],"topics":["調酒","威士忌"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"品酒","forumAlias":"alcohol","school":"東吳大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":true,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":36}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/G4r4UtF.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"349139ca-fc27-4996-8062-f09593a50f9f","url":"https://i.imgur.com/G4r4UtFl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/G4r4UtFl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/G4r4UtFl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-11-04T14:39:18.019Z","updatedAt":"2019-11-04T14:39:18.019Z"},{"id":"349139ca-fc27-4996-8062-f09593a50f9f","url":"https://i.imgur.com/G4r4UtF.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/G4r4UtF","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/G4r4UtFl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-11-04T14:39:18.019Z","update